{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/learn-javascript/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bwake blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e9c9bafc-9b28-5763-8455-47e82dc3b094","excerpt":"Linking JavaScript to your HTML Method 1 Adding scripts tag to your HTML at the end of the body tag Method 2 Linking an external javaScript file to your HTML…","html":"<h2>Linking JavaScript to your HTML</h2>\n<h4>Method 1</h4>\n<p>Adding scripts tag to your HTML at the end of the body tag</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      JavaScript code goes here\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h4>Method 2</h4>\n<p>Linking an external javaScript file to your HTML</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>./path/index.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>JavaScript Datatypes</h2>\n<h3>Primitive Datatypes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>String</li>\n<li>Number</li>\n<li>Boolean</li>\n<li>Null</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Reference types</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Array</li>\n<li>Object</li>\n<li>Function</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Variables</h3>\n<p>Variables are containers that store data values</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Davis\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//String</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">25467</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Number</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> isCool <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Boolean</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> stranger <span class=\"token comment\">//undefined value</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> age <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>variables declared with var and let can be re-assigned</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bwake\"</span>\n    id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">74621</span>\n    isCool <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n    stranger <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//nothing</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can also concatenate strings with with variables</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> complement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"is cool\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Lets log the above variables on the console, you can use browsers console or run the file on the terminal with node</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>isCool<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>stranger<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> complement<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Math Operations</h3>\n<p>JavaScript supports many many operations, here are the basic ones in their shortest form</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    id <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    id <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    id <span class=\"token operator\">*=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    id <span class=\"token operator\">/=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    id  <span class=\"token operator\">%=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Arrays</h3>\n<p>Arrays are used to store multiple values in a single variable</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'Dodge'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Duck'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Dive'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'Done'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//a numbered list of items</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Davis'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Add array to top of the stack</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Remove the item on top of the stack</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">unshift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Dan'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Add item to the bottom of the stack</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Remove item from the bottom of the list</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">splice</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Donstesh\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Replace items in the array</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">reverse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">indexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Duck'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Duck'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//indexOf Return index of the item else returns -1 counting from the start</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//lastIndexOf Return index of the item else returns -1 counting from the end</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Objects</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> myObject<span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'Davis'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    age<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    isCool<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    myObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">34875</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    myObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lastName\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'bwake'</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>myObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Functions</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Davis'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>if … if else statements</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>age <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'You are twenty years old'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>age<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'youre 19 years old or younger'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'youre above 20 years old'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>age<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> age<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'youre between 11 and 30 age bracket'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>age<span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token string\">'bwake'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' youre '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> age <span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token string\">' years old'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//Ternary operator</span>\n    name <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token string\">'bwake'</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'I dont know you '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//Falsey(values that evaluate to false) => false, null,undefined, 0, \"\",'', NaN</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//Comparison operators => &lt;, &lt;=, >, >=, ==, !=, !==</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//Binary logical operators => &amp;&amp;, ||</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Learn JavaScript","date":"December 27, 2018","description":"JavaScript is a scripting language developed to add functionality in the browser. It's use nowdays extends building mobile apps, creating servers, building desktop apps etc"}},"previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/git-cheat-sheet/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git Cheat Sheet"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"e9c9bafc-9b28-5763-8455-47e82dc3b094","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":"4e839092-fc6c-5e30-ad58-251eee9277af"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}